<p>英 /'saɪkl/    美 /'saɪkl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt (使) 循环：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The water is cycled through the machine and reused.
这些水通过机器循环后再使用。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-bre">2.★ <strong>(BrE) 骑自行车 / 摩托车：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s frightening to be cycling to work in a sandstorm.
在沙尘暴天气里骑车去上班很可怕。</p><footer>外研③ – 4</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
